Now, dance!

3
00:00:01.310 --> 00:00:02.480
Drink!

4
00:00:02.810 --> 00:00:05.310
Eat! Don't be shy!

5
00:00:44.890 --> 00:00:48.480
Oh, I feel lighter without flesh
to weigh me down.

6
00:00:48.480 --> 00:00:51.470
I mean, I don't have any flesh.

7
00:00:51.470 --> 00:00:53.990
Because I'm just a skeleton.

8
00:00:53.990 --> 00:00:57.810
There's no point if I'm the only one
who hears the skull joke...

9
00:00:57.810 --> 00:00:59.830
Time to start searching!

10
00:01:19.710 --> 00:01:22.640
A suspicious reinforced door...

11
00:01:22.640 --> 00:01:24.180
Something smells off here.

12
00:01:24.520 --> 00:01:26.410
Not that I have a nose.

13
00:01:30.370 --> 00:01:33.410
What are those dolls?

14
00:01:36.490 --> 00:01:39.330
A poneglyph?!

