19
00:03:24.270 --> 00:03:28.080
Soba Mask

20
00:03:30.230 --> 00:03:33.520
Hegemony!

21
00:03:35.030 --> 00:03:37.150
We've lost the picture!

22
00:03:37.150 --> 00:03:40.360
Switch to a different camera already!

23
00:03:42.070 --> 00:03:42.860
Honestly...

24
00:03:47.490 --> 00:03:48.470
What?!

25
00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:56.420
They broke through the last line of defense
and are now climbing up the falls!

26
00:03:56.590 --> 00:03:58.550
Whaaat?!

27
00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:04.260
Keep going!

28
00:04:05.340 --> 00:04:07.690
The fish are climbing the waterfalls!

29
00:04:08.210 --> 00:04:11.370
It's lickety unbelievable.

30
00:04:11.370 --> 00:04:14.400
Dammit! What are you morons doing?!

31
00:04:14.400 --> 00:04:17.270
Don't let them set foot on the island!

32
00:04:17.270 --> 00:04:21.190
But we have no troops at the top of the falls!

33
00:04:21.190 --> 00:04:24.200
Plus, the enemy is immensely powerful!

34
00:04:24.570 --> 00:04:28.450
We don't have time to mobilize weapons
that could take them down!

35
00:04:29.510 --> 00:04:31.410
Don't panic!

36
00:04:32.850 --> 00:04:33.870
Viceroy Kaido!

37
00:04:37.010 --> 00:04:42.630
Damn Linlin... She even
brought her brats with her.

38
00:04:48.720 --> 00:04:51.600
Get your shit together, boys!

39
00:04:57.690 --> 00:05:01.690
This'll be an all-out war!

40
00:05:08.310 --> 00:05:10.910
We don't have to sit here and wait for them.

41
00:05:36.450 --> 00:05:39.560
Hmph! What's taking them so long
to handle a single ship?!

42
00:05:40.730 --> 00:05:43.570
Ancient Saur Saur Fruit:
Pteranodon

43
00:05:43.820 --> 00:05:44.860
I'll deal with it!

44
00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:53.740
We're near the top!

45
00:05:54.750 --> 00:05:56.710
We're almost there!

46
00:05:57.620 --> 00:06:00.750
Here I am, Kaido!

47
00:06:02.380 --> 00:06:03.590
What's that?!

48
00:06:05.550 --> 00:06:08.180
Is that King?!

49
00:06:08.180 --> 00:06:09.590
A pteranodon?!

50
00:06:09.890 --> 00:06:11.470
Shoot him down!

51
00:06:24.400 --> 00:06:26.400
He fled in disgrace!

52
00:06:44.410 --> 00:06:47.670
We made it to Wano!

53
00:06:47.670 --> 00:06:51.840
Now, let's kill Straw Hat!

54
00:06:53.850 --> 00:06:55.100
He's still here!

55
00:07:01.870 --> 00:07:03.190
No way!

56
00:07:08.780 --> 00:07:09.490
It can't be!

57
00:07:17.910 --> 00:07:20.960
King, you killjoy!

58
00:07:23.210 --> 00:07:26.250
I won't let you set foot in Wano!

59
00:07:29.850 --> 00:07:31.880
Dammit!

60
00:07:31.880 --> 00:07:32.970
Mama!

61
00:07:38.870 --> 00:07:42.060
Hmph! Get swallowed by the sea.

62
00:08:03.850 --> 00:08:06.170
Hurry up, Franosuke!

63
00:08:06.170 --> 00:08:09.460
Hey, why do we have to run?!

64
00:08:09.850 --> 00:08:12.220
They're after Sangoro the soba cook!

65
00:08:12.690 --> 00:08:18.760
But you helped that soba cook take down
a member of the Kyoshiro Family!

66
00:08:23.430 --> 00:08:24.560
Sorry, I couldn't resist!

67
00:08:26.410 --> 00:08:28.320
They're linked to Orochi.

68
00:08:28.320 --> 00:08:33.400
So they sent members of the Beast Pirates'
Soaring Six out for revenge!

69
00:08:35.740 --> 00:08:39.660
Oh no! The bad guys?! Damn it!

70
00:08:45.850 --> 00:08:48.720
Thank goodness. It's you guys.

71
00:08:48.720 --> 00:08:50.750
It's not safe here. This way!

72
00:08:50.750 --> 00:08:52.170
Okay!

73
00:08:52.170 --> 00:08:56.290
This is bad. It doesn't matter
what triggered this anymore.

74
00:08:56.290 --> 00:08:59.230
If any of you get caught and exposed,

75
00:08:59.230 --> 00:09:00.680
things will get dicey.

76
00:09:01.650 --> 00:09:04.350
They'll start searching for
the rest of your crew!

77
00:09:04.350 --> 00:09:07.900
Oh, no! Nami and Robin would be in danger!

78
00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:11.150
Let's hope they stick to you three!

79
00:09:12.110 --> 00:09:15.200
But the moment they discover
your ties to the Kozuki Clan,

80
00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:18.530
this twenty-year plan for
vengeance will be ruined!

81
00:09:19.200 --> 00:09:20.330
In fact...

82
00:09:21.450 --> 00:09:23.750
even if you get caught and tortured...

83
00:09:23.750 --> 00:09:25.120
Yeah...?

84
00:09:25.120 --> 00:09:29.080
...you mustn't tell them about
the samurai or the minks.

85
00:09:30.870 --> 00:09:32.460
Just keep quiet and...

86
00:09:32.850 --> 00:09:34.050
let them kill you!

87
00:09:34.050 --> 00:09:35.470
You're terrible!

88
00:09:35.470 --> 00:09:38.090
Luffy wouldn't say something like that!

89
00:09:38.090 --> 00:09:39.800
I'm more practical.

90
00:09:39.800 --> 00:09:42.850
It's fine if they don't know it's us, right?

91
00:09:42.850 --> 00:09:44.490
Well, then...

92
00:09:49.370 --> 00:09:51.860
Why don't we fight with our faces hidden?!

93
00:09:55.250 --> 00:09:57.110
Avoid fighting for now.

94
00:09:57.110 --> 00:09:59.820
Stop acting like you're our captain!

95
00:09:59.820 --> 00:10:01.870
If I get caught...

96
00:10:01.870 --> 00:10:04.330
I'll tell them everything just to get away!

97
00:10:04.330 --> 00:10:05.910
Screw you!

98
00:10:06.260 --> 00:10:07.930
Then I'll protect you at any cost!

99
00:10:07.930 --> 00:10:09.220
Yes!

100
00:10:09.220 --> 00:10:10.710
Some friendship!

101
00:10:20.630 --> 00:10:21.550
It's a lady!

102
00:10:29.390 --> 00:10:32.440
Soba Shop

103
00:10:33.090 --> 00:10:34.340
That's not good!

104
00:10:34.340 --> 00:10:36.070
Someone's already after us?!

105
00:10:52.390 --> 00:10:55.670
Please stop! We have nothing to do with this!

106
00:11:00.220 --> 00:11:04.730
We serve soba, but we have nothing
to do with Sangoro the soba cook!

107
00:11:04.730 --> 00:11:06.850
How could you destroy our shop?!

108
00:11:06.850 --> 00:11:09.670
We can't stay in the city without it!

109
00:11:13.790 --> 00:11:18.030
If you wanna blame someone,
blame that fool Sangoro.

110
00:11:20.210 --> 00:11:22.940
Tell me where I can find more soba shops!

111
00:11:22.940 --> 00:11:27.790
Or, call out for Sangoro!

112
00:11:28.500 --> 00:11:31.750
That jackass messed with the Kyoshiro Family!

113
00:11:33.460 --> 00:11:36.710
If you refuse...

114
00:11:37.210 --> 00:11:39.090
I'll eat you, too!

115
00:11:42.300 --> 00:11:45.270
Sangoro!

116
00:11:45.560 --> 00:11:47.640
Sangoro!

117
00:11:51.640 --> 00:11:53.310
Hey!

118
00:11:53.870 --> 00:11:56.490
Sangoro, show yourself!

119
00:12:00.280 --> 00:12:02.790
– Sangoro!
– Sangoro!

120
00:12:02.790 --> 00:12:05.170
Maybe it's no use.

121
00:12:07.130 --> 00:12:10.160
If he's a coward, he'll never show himself!

122
00:12:10.160 --> 00:12:12.970
Sangoro!

123
00:12:14.410 --> 00:12:19.000
Oh, I wanna eat something sweet now!

124
00:12:19.400 --> 00:12:21.750
They're playing dirty!

125
00:12:22.290 --> 00:12:24.130
Right now, our priority is escaping!

126
00:12:26.090 --> 00:12:27.870
There's no way...

127
00:12:28.670 --> 00:12:30.810
I can do that!

128
00:12:33.510 --> 00:12:36.020
Hey, wait, Sanji!

129
00:12:37.130 --> 00:12:39.820
Stop it! We have nothing to do with him!

130
00:12:40.180 --> 00:12:42.290
Then, call out for him...

131
00:12:42.290 --> 00:12:43.900
all of you!

132
00:12:45.780 --> 00:12:48.490
Call for Sangoro, the soba cook!

133
00:12:56.150 --> 00:12:57.290
I'm...

134
00:12:58.410 --> 00:13:00.550
here!

135
00:13:01.380 --> 00:13:03.550
Diable Jambe:

136
00:13:03.550 --> 00:13:05.630
Concassé!

137
00:13:20.730 --> 00:13:22.590
That's him...

138
00:13:22.590 --> 00:13:23.490
He's...

139
00:13:23.490 --> 00:13:26.350
Sangoro of the Special Soba!

140
00:13:32.490 --> 00:13:34.510
So you're the soba cook...

141
00:13:35.930 --> 00:13:40.210
You showed up.
Don't make it any harder on me.

142
00:13:40.770 --> 00:13:46.310
Hey, this is Page One. I found the target
on the sixth block of district two!

143
00:13:46.310 --> 00:13:49.390
Roger! We'll be there as soon as we can.

144
00:13:51.330 --> 00:13:53.810
You can't escape now!

145
00:13:54.650 --> 00:13:56.870
Dinosaur powers, huh?

146
00:14:02.630 --> 00:14:03.820
You asshole...

147
00:14:08.610 --> 00:14:10.370
What are you doing, Sangoro?!

148
00:14:10.710 --> 00:14:14.490
Let it go! We're done for
if Drake and Hawkins come!

149
00:14:15.350 --> 00:14:16.580
I know.

150
00:14:23.190 --> 00:14:24.000
That said...

151
00:14:24.790 --> 00:14:27.220
this guy has no idea who I am.

152
00:14:27.220 --> 00:14:30.700
No one will find me out, and I won't get hurt!

153
00:14:30.700 --> 00:14:33.310
This loser will go down in an instant.

154
00:14:41.490 --> 00:14:43.730
Yeah, having more allies is nice...

155
00:14:45.400 --> 00:14:48.570
but reducing the numbers on
the other side helps, too.

156
00:14:49.670 --> 00:14:52.120
Stop talking gibberish!

157
00:15:00.230 --> 00:15:02.670
Guys, go on ahead!

158
00:15:02.670 --> 00:15:03.590
– What?
– What?

159
00:15:11.550 --> 00:15:13.730
It'll be fine as long as...

160
00:15:19.030 --> 00:15:21.520
I hide my identity, right?

161
00:15:21.520 --> 00:15:23.770
The soba cook really showed up?!

162
00:15:23.770 --> 00:15:26.070
Is he stupid?! Does he wanna die?!

163
00:15:28.970 --> 00:15:31.860
This is the perfect time to transform.

164
00:15:34.210 --> 00:15:37.370
What's that? Is it a can of something?

165
00:15:39.370 --> 00:15:45.890
Even if wear this, I won't be
like the members of Germa!

166
00:15:47.070 --> 00:15:49.760
I'm just trying it on for size.

167
00:15:50.410 --> 00:15:53.170
He should've abandoned the town.

168
00:15:53.170 --> 00:15:56.010
What's he gonna do?!

169
00:15:56.470 --> 00:15:58.750
We're about to fight an emperor.

170
00:15:59.850 --> 00:16:04.480
My stubbornness runs the risk of
getting in the way of saving someone.

171
00:16:04.480 --> 00:16:09.400
But if I swallow my pride, then maybe
I can rush to someone's rescue.

172
00:16:09.400 --> 00:16:12.620
Even more gibberish!

173
00:16:16.570 --> 00:16:20.750
Especially if this thing powers me up!

174
00:16:21.830 --> 00:16:22.750
Here I go!

175
00:16:50.360 --> 00:16:52.570
What are you doing?

176
00:16:52.890 --> 00:16:55.030
You just changed in midair?

177
00:16:55.460 --> 00:16:56.780
Black Leg...

178
00:16:56.780 --> 00:17:01.040
Oh, he transformed?! How super!

179
00:17:01.130 --> 00:17:03.710
Cool! How does it work?!

180
00:17:04.550 --> 00:17:08.590
Wait. I know that costume from somewhere...

181
00:17:12.610 --> 00:17:14.970
Oh, yeah! But...

182
00:17:15.460 --> 00:17:19.140
how did he get that suit?!

183
00:17:19.140 --> 00:17:23.220
That's definitely an enemy of Sora,
Warrior of the Sea!

184
00:17:24.510 --> 00:17:28.310
He's the number three member
of the evil army, Germa 66!

185
00:17:28.310 --> 00:17:29.970
Stealth Black!

186
00:17:32.810 --> 00:17:34.780
Hey, why do you know so much about it?!

187
00:17:35.130 --> 00:17:38.070
It's only natural! Everyone from
the North Blue knows!

188
00:17:38.560 --> 00:17:40.570
Whatever!

189
00:17:40.570 --> 00:17:44.950
Listen! Never call me
Germa again! Understood?!

190
00:17:45.450 --> 00:17:49.560
I was a devoted fan of Sora,
Warrior of the Sea!

191
00:17:49.560 --> 00:17:53.170
I hated Germa; they were deplorable villains.

192
00:17:53.170 --> 00:17:54.470
I hate them, too!

193
00:17:54.470 --> 00:17:55.670
Hey, you!

194
00:17:56.340 --> 00:18:00.350
You're no ordinary soba cook...

195
00:18:00.350 --> 00:18:01.890
Who are you?!

196
00:18:06.250 --> 00:18:07.690
I am...

197
00:18:11.920 --> 00:18:15.170
Soba Mask

198
00:18:12.410 --> 00:18:14.490
Soba Mask!

199
00:18:16.590 --> 00:18:18.320
Soba Mask...

200
00:18:18.320 --> 00:18:21.070
No... He's definitely Germa.

201
00:18:22.410 --> 00:18:25.990
That's awful! Change your name!

202
00:18:25.990 --> 00:18:28.870
Please let us name you!

203
00:18:28.870 --> 00:18:33.630
Did you say Soba Mask?! Don't mess with me!

204
00:18:40.720 --> 00:18:43.840
Where'd he go?

205
00:18:43.840 --> 00:18:45.220
What?!

206
00:18:45.220 --> 00:18:47.980
He's floating in midair!

207
00:18:49.510 --> 00:18:50.900
How's that possible?!

208
00:18:50.900 --> 00:18:55.650
No doubt about it...
That's Germa tech, all right.

209
00:18:55.650 --> 00:18:59.570
The devices on their heels
allow them to float...

210
00:18:59.570 --> 00:19:01.280
Yeah, he has to be...

211
00:19:03.570 --> 00:19:05.030
That's awesome!

212
00:19:07.070 --> 00:19:09.910
This is child's play!

213
00:19:42.570 --> 00:19:44.660
Way to go, Soba Mask!

214
00:19:53.120 --> 00:19:57.250
Your attacks are so annoying...
They piss me off!

215
00:20:09.890 --> 00:20:11.560
What the hell is this?!

216
00:20:12.790 --> 00:20:14.150
Wow!

217
00:20:14.150 --> 00:20:16.270
His punch can't get through!

218
00:20:16.820 --> 00:20:19.130
The capes worn by Germa 66...

219
00:20:19.850 --> 00:20:22.030
can become solid shields...

220
00:20:26.510 --> 00:20:30.330
I know your moves! Your attacks
won't work a second time!

221
00:20:33.120 --> 00:20:34.850
Oh no!

222
00:20:36.510 --> 00:20:41.170
The real Stealth Black would've used
a certain something by now...

223
00:20:42.350 --> 00:20:44.220
I won't let you get away now!

224
00:20:47.100 --> 00:20:48.100
He disappeared?!

225
00:20:48.580 --> 00:20:50.140
No way!

226
00:20:51.350 --> 00:20:55.530
People can't just vanish!
Where is he?! Where'd he go?!

227
00:20:55.530 --> 00:20:57.610
Get out here!

228
00:20:57.610 --> 00:20:59.320
I thought so.

229
00:21:11.030 --> 00:21:13.680
Whoa! Huh? Where is he?!

230
00:21:13.680 --> 00:21:15.420
He's moving too fast to see!

231
00:21:15.850 --> 00:21:21.130
No, that's a special ability of
Germa 66's Stealth Black...

232
00:21:21.130 --> 00:21:25.430
He became invisible by projecting
the background over his body!

233
00:21:27.850 --> 00:21:31.930
Even Sora, Warrior of the Sea,
had quite a hard time with him...

234
00:21:36.130 --> 00:21:38.030
Germa scum...!

235
00:21:38.030 --> 00:21:40.430
Whose side are you on?!

236
00:21:40.430 --> 00:21:43.200
You know way too much about this!

237
00:21:43.200 --> 00:21:45.360
I'm from the North Blue; it's a given.

238
00:21:53.870 --> 00:21:58.120
What's with this suit?! Did I disappear?!

239
00:21:59.190 --> 00:22:01.710
It's just like the Clear-Clear Fruit?!

240
00:22:02.590 --> 00:22:07.180
Devil Fruits

241
00:22:03.290 --> 00:22:07.180
It's the devil fruit I've always
dreamed of having...

242
00:22:07.710 --> 00:22:11.530
With the Clear-Clear Fruit,
I could become invisible.

243
00:22:12.430 --> 00:22:15.250
The dream that fell to pieces...

244
00:22:16.850 --> 00:22:21.440
That's right. You stole a dream from me!

245
00:22:21.830 --> 00:22:25.890
I don't remember doing anything
like that. You must be mistaken.

246
00:22:26.470 --> 00:22:31.450
I wanted to become the invisible man!

247
00:22:31.450 --> 00:22:38.080
But you ate the Clear-Clear Fruit,
crushing one of my dreams, got it?!

248
00:22:38.080 --> 00:22:40.460
Wh-What?!

249
00:22:40.500 --> 00:22:42.960
– That's not his fault!
– That's not his fault!

250
00:22:43.970 --> 00:22:46.460
The dream that fell to pieces...

251
00:22:46.880 --> 00:22:51.520
is now possible because of
the Germa tech I despised?

252
00:22:51.520 --> 00:22:53.050
How ironic...

253
00:22:55.410 --> 00:22:58.610
But this ability will definitely be useful...

254
00:22:59.250 --> 00:23:01.650
I can make use of this in the women's bath...

255
00:23:01.650 --> 00:23:02.730
No, no!

256
00:23:03.770 --> 00:23:08.240
I can use this to protect
my friends! What a dilemma!

257
00:23:20.370 --> 00:23:25.040
An invisible man...?
Mighty fishy, if you ask me...

258
00:23:25.750 --> 00:23:28.460
Just who are you?!

259
00:23:28.460 --> 00:23:33.930
This form seems better suited to fighting
an opponent that moves around so much.

260
00:23:35.390 --> 00:23:38.370
At first I was gonna make you suffer,

261
00:23:38.370 --> 00:23:41.950
but I guess I'd better just kill you.

262
00:24:01.490 --> 00:24:03.330
Hey, Jaggy!

263
00:24:07.410 --> 00:24:10.380
I bet you still have some dumplings!

264
00:24:10.780 --> 00:24:13.710
Come on, Jaggy! Don't pretend to be asleep!

265
00:24:16.550 --> 00:24:19.030
I know you can hear me, Jaggy!

266
00:24:38.710 --> 00:24:42.090
This room is quite old and mysterious...

267
00:24:43.210 --> 00:24:46.010
This country has been isolated for centuries...

268
00:24:50.570 --> 00:24:53.560
And the poneglyphs were invented here.

269
00:24:53.560 --> 00:24:55.650
I'm sure there's one here.

270
00:24:57.050 --> 00:24:59.970
There must be a hidden door somewhere...

271
00:25:04.130 --> 00:25:06.230
Looking for something?

272
00:25:08.290 --> 00:25:10.780
No way! How did I miss this?!

273
00:25:14.410 --> 00:25:15.740
Good!

274
00:25:16.110 --> 00:25:18.370
Good, good, good, good...

275
00:25:19.350 --> 00:25:23.500
Komurasaki, play that one tune!

276
00:25:23.500 --> 00:25:26.190
As you wish...

277
00:25:34.590 --> 00:25:38.070
Kuri Beach

278
00:25:43.060 --> 00:25:46.390
Otama, let's have a fair fight!

279
00:25:46.390 --> 00:25:49.610
I could ask for nothing better, Chopperemon!

280
00:25:52.730 --> 00:25:55.490
Ninpo: Tree Leaf Technique!

281
00:25:56.360 --> 00:25:57.200
Ninpo...

282
00:25:59.490 --> 00:26:02.080
Zigzag Run!

283
00:26:02.080 --> 00:26:03.830
Take this!

284
00:26:14.450 --> 00:26:18.260
I have a hard road ahead if I'm
gonna be a bewitching kunoichi.

285
00:26:20.650 --> 00:26:23.510
I managed to dodge everything...

286
00:26:24.870 --> 00:26:26.730
Excellent work, both of you!

287
00:26:26.730 --> 00:26:30.410
I'm still worried about Big Bro Luffy...

288
00:26:30.410 --> 00:26:33.770
Don't worry! He'll be all right!

289
00:26:39.610 --> 00:26:44.710
Raizo hasn't reported back either.
It's difficult to not be anxious...

290
00:26:44.710 --> 00:26:51.090
Master said that no one has ever
escaped the prison in Udon...

291
00:26:51.090 --> 00:26:54.500
I said he'll be fine! Nin-nin!

292
00:26:54.500 --> 00:26:57.880
For now, all we can do is train ourselves!

293
00:26:58.290 --> 00:27:00.930
Ninpo: Tree Climb Technique!

294
00:27:00.930 --> 00:27:02.180
Nin! Nin-nin!

295
00:27:02.180 --> 00:27:05.640
Were I to possess greater strength,
I would save him immediately.

296
00:27:06.270 --> 00:27:07.000
Nin!

297
00:27:08.270 --> 00:27:09.590
Oh?

298
00:27:10.270 --> 00:27:13.110
What is that?

299
00:27:14.930 --> 00:27:16.400
Nin! Nin!

300
00:27:21.740 --> 00:27:23.030
It's curious...

301
00:27:23.030 --> 00:27:28.160
Whenever Big Sis Komurasaki plays
that music, she puts on that mask.

302
00:27:32.920 --> 00:27:36.590
That's it! That's it! That's the song!

303
00:27:36.960 --> 00:27:38.590
I love it!

304
00:27:43.140 --> 00:27:47.430
It's a mistake to act suspiciously
in the presence of ninja.

305
00:27:49.310 --> 00:27:51.190
How naive!

306
00:27:53.020 --> 00:27:55.690
Don't you know what ninja are?

307
00:27:57.270 --> 00:27:59.280
She could be from overseas.

308
00:28:05.700 --> 00:28:12.640
Orochi's Oniwabanshu
The personal Ninja Squad of the Shogun of Wano

309
00:28:14.790 --> 00:28:17.180
Why, hello there.

310
00:28:17.180 --> 00:28:19.300
You're quite the troublesome geisha...

311
00:28:20.510 --> 00:28:22.470
I'll give you a chance to explain.

312
00:28:24.430 --> 00:28:28.910
Fukurokuju
Head of the Oniwabanshu

313
00:28:24.850 --> 00:28:28.390
However, you'll only get the one chance.

314
00:28:55.210 --> 00:28:57.590
You okay, Sangoro?!

315
00:28:57.590 --> 00:29:01.090
Those with ancient-type abilities
sure are powerful. However...

316
00:29:01.490 --> 00:29:04.710
it's not enough to beat Stealth Black.

317
00:29:11.330 --> 00:29:15.190
It hurts a bit, but this thing is durable.

318
00:29:17.950 --> 00:29:20.940
The capital can't take much more, though.

319
00:29:24.710 --> 00:29:28.260
Hey! Why are we leaving Sangoro behind?!

320
00:29:28.260 --> 00:29:30.210
He told us to go on ahead.

321
00:29:30.210 --> 00:29:32.450
I mean, he did, but still...!

322
00:29:34.530 --> 00:29:39.280
All right, time to deliver
his corpse to Boss Kyoshiro.

323
00:29:39.280 --> 00:29:41.130
Who the hell was he anyway?

324
00:29:50.100 --> 00:29:54.020
Others will come after us,
and things will get tricky.

325
00:29:54.690 --> 00:29:58.900
We should leave the capital
for now. Let's head to Ebisu!

326
00:30:31.430 --> 00:30:35.390
Shooting Star Soba Kick!

327
00:30:38.520 --> 00:30:39.690
What?!

328
00:30:59.630 --> 00:31:01.920
Tch! He's pretty tough.

329
00:31:05.370 --> 00:31:06.420
Where are you?!

330
00:31:06.750 --> 00:31:11.890
Where did you go?!
Show yourself, Soba Mask!

331
00:31:12.990 --> 00:31:15.180
Soba Mask, huh?

332
00:31:15.580 --> 00:31:19.610
I should ask Franosuke and Usohachi
to redesign this!

333
00:31:31.590 --> 00:31:34.660
What is it?! A person?!

334
00:31:34.660 --> 00:31:37.570
What an enormous person...!

335
00:31:38.930 --> 00:31:41.500
Still smaller than a giant, though!

336
00:31:41.500 --> 00:31:45.530
Wh-Who do you think is bigger?
Kaido or this person?

337
00:31:46.050 --> 00:31:49.170
Is it a woman?

338
00:31:55.220 --> 00:31:56.220
No way!

339
00:32:07.820 --> 00:32:09.860
Big Mo–

340
00:32:10.190 --> 00:32:13.550
Big Mom (Charlotte Linlin)
Captain of the Big Mom Pirates

341
00:32:15.470 --> 00:32:17.050
What's the matter?

342
00:32:18.010 --> 00:32:20.080
Don't speak! You'll wake her up!

343
00:32:20.500 --> 00:32:23.330
We've got to run!
It's all over if she wakes up!

344
00:32:23.920 --> 00:32:29.180
No, it's too late! Running won't
work if she's followed us here.

345
00:32:29.180 --> 00:32:31.230
What are you talking about?

346
00:32:31.230 --> 00:32:34.180
Do you know who she is?

347
00:32:34.180 --> 00:32:36.890
Everyone knows her! She's...

348
00:32:38.670 --> 00:32:40.640
Whaaat?!

349
00:32:41.130 --> 00:32:43.480
She is the infamous Big Mom?!

350
00:32:43.480 --> 00:32:44.730
You're too loud!

351
00:32:46.330 --> 00:32:48.560
Who is Big Mom?

352
00:32:48.560 --> 00:32:50.780
I'll tell you later!

353
00:32:56.450 --> 00:32:59.540
I'll finish her off myself!

354
00:32:59.540 --> 00:33:02.430
That's right! Think of her as Kaido!

355
00:33:02.430 --> 00:33:04.210
She's the same as Kaido!

356
00:33:12.720 --> 00:33:14.590
I-It's too late!

357
00:33:14.590 --> 00:33:17.350
Just run for it!

358
00:33:25.050 --> 00:33:27.250
Where...?

359
00:33:28.470 --> 00:33:31.850
Where... am I?

360
00:33:41.830 --> 00:33:43.950
Who...

361
00:33:46.030 --> 00:33:47.500
am I?!

362
00:34:00.250 --> 00:34:01.400
Huh?!
